Jeff Hordley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeff_Hordley 0 Jeff Hordley (born Jeffrey Thomas Percy, 7 March 1970 in Crumpsall, Manchester) is an English actor most notable for playing Cain Dingle in ITV's long-running soap opera Emmerdale.
